; Coverage for xact.cc line 1037 (check warning in auto_xact)
; When a check expression evaluates to false, a warning is issued
; but processing continues.

= Expenses
    check amount < 0
    (Budget)    -1

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Test                  Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
                                (Budget)                    $-10.00      $-10.00
__ERROR__
Warning: "$FILE", line 9: Transaction check failed: (amount < {0})
  (check expression at "$FILE", line 5)
end test
